>

<p style=3D"color:#333">By the time we returned home, he owned a copy. And =
much to my surprise, he was so taken by its simple affirmations, like =E2=
=80=9Cdon=E2=80=99t take anything personally=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Calways d=
